table_trans: Setting up sheds for automatic reeling machines (ARMs) (minimum 400 ends or 40 basins)
A subsidy of 50% of the cost of construction or ₹40.00 lakh, whichever is less, will be provided as per the DSR rate.
Setting up sheds for Automated Relling Machines (ARMs) (minimum 200 ends or 20 basins)
A subsidy of 50% of the DSR rate or ₹20.00 lakh, whichever is less, will be provided.
Setting up sheds for Automated Relling Machines (ARMs) (minimum 120 ends or 12 basins)
A subsidy of 50% of the DSR rate or ₹15.00 lakh, whichever is less, will be provided.
Setting up of sheds for multi-ends reeling machines (minimum 100 ends 10 basins)
The subsidy will be 50% of the DSR rate or ₹3 lakh whichever is less.
Setting up of shed for Vetting Machine
The subsidy will be 50% of the DSR rate or ₹6 lakh, whichever is less.
